title: 148:  Wild Card preview, best coaching vacancies, National Championship preview
itunes:title: 148:  Wild Card preview, best coaching vacancies, National Championship preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the upcoming slate of Wild Card playoff games. The duo also review the current NFL head coaching vacancies and which available jobs are the most attractive. Moving to the college football scene, DJ and Bucky also preview the NCAA National Championship and take a look back at the best bowl games.
